# JustPlanner — Agent Rules

## Stack

**Frontend:**
- React 19 + TypeScript
- Vite (dev/build)
- Lucide React (icons)
- Sentry (error tracking)
- mobile-drag-drop (touch support)

**Backend:**
- Node.js + Express (ES Modules)
- PostgreSQL (pg driver)
- JWT auth + Passport Google OAuth
- YooKassa (payments)
- node-cron (scheduled tasks)
- nodemailer (emails)
- bcrypt (password hashing)

**DevOps:**
- PM2 (process manager)
- Nginx (reverse proxy)
- GitHub Actions (CI/CD)
- VPS: 5.35.94.142

## Architecture

```
justplanner/
├── index.tsx                    # React entry point
├── App.tsx                      # Main app component (50KB, monolithic)
├── types.ts                     # Global TypeScript types
├── api.ts                       # API client (tasks, settings)
├── utils.ts                     # Date utils, holidays
├── vite.config.ts               # Proxy /api → :3001
│
├── components/                  # UI components
│   ├── AuthModal.tsx
│   ├── TaskModal.tsx
│   ├── SettingsModal.tsx
│   ├── Column.tsx
│   ├── TaskItem.tsx
│   ├── LandingPage.tsx
│   ├── FeaturesPage.tsx
│   ├── PricingPage.tsx
│   └── Legal/
│
├── contexts/                    # React Contexts
│   ├── AuthContext.tsx
│   └── SettingsContext.tsx
│
├── billing/                     # Billing module (frontend)
│   ├── BillingContext.tsx
│   ├── api.ts
│   ├── types.ts
│   └── components/
│
├── annual-offer/                # Annual offer module
│   ├── AnnualOfferModal.tsx
│   ├── AnnualOfferWidget.tsx
│   └── useCountdown.ts
│
└── server/                      # Backend
    ├── index.js                 # Express app
    ├── config/db.js             # PostgreSQL pool
    ├── middleware/auth.js       # JWT middleware
    ├── models/                  # User, Task models
    ├── routes/                  # auth, tasks, settings, admin
    ├── billing/                 # YooKassa, renewals, routes
    ├── utils/                   # email, telegram
    └── tests/                   # smoke-test, daily-report, health-cron
```

**Patterns:**
- Monolithic App.tsx with inline state management
- React Context for auth, settings, billing
- ES Modules throughout (type: module)
- PostgreSQL with raw SQL queries (no ORM)
- Cron jobs for renewals, reminders, tests

## Conventions

**Naming:**
- Components: PascalCase (.tsx)
- Utils/API: camelCase (.ts, .js)
- React hooks: `use` prefix
- DB columns: snake_case
- API routes: kebab-case URLs

**Code style:**
- React functional components
- Named exports preferred (some default exports in models)
- Inline type definitions in .tsx files
- Async/await (no .then chains)
- Error handling with try/catch

**DB conventions:**
- Table names: plural (users, tasks, payments, subscriptions)
- Primary key: `id SERIAL`
- Foreign keys: `user_id INTEGER`
- Timestamps: `created_at`, `updated_at`, `last_login`
- Booleans: `is_verified`, `is_annual`, `auto_renew`

**API conventions:**
- Auth: JWT in cookies + Authorization header
- Response format: JSON `{ data }` or `{ error }`
- Protected routes use `authenticateToken` middleware
- Errors: appropriate HTTP status codes

## Key Files

**Entry points:**
- `index.tsx` — React app bootstrap
- `App.tsx` — Main UI logic (tasks, calendar, drag-drop)
- `server/index.js` — Express server, routes, cron jobs

**Critical modules:**
- `contexts/AuthContext.tsx` — Login, register, Google OAuth
- `billing/BillingContext.tsx` — Subscription state
- `server/billing/renewal.js` — Auto-renewal cron (3:00 MSK daily)
- `server/utils/telegram.js` — Notifications + bot polling
- `server/utils/email.js` — Welcome + reminder emails

**Config:**
- `vite.config.ts` — Proxy setup
- `ecosystem.config.js` — PM2 config
- `server/.env` — All secrets (not in repo)
- `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` — CI/CD pipeline

**DB Schema:**
- `server/schema.sql` — users, tasks
- `server/billing/schema.sql` — subscriptions, payments

**Tests:**
- `server/tests/smoke-test.js` — 11 checks, runs every 5 min
- `server/tests/daily-report.js` — Telegram report at 09:00 MSK

